VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'that once I turn on here the wireframe and select it that it\'s obviously not a clean wireframe. So, if you\'re looking for this, then you [music] might need to further treat it on the line to retopologize it and so on. But, this is obviously not the purpose here from this'

[08:52] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'model because it serves here, you know, as a visual representation in our 3D scene. So, it can be used for background assets, and in case you still would like to use it as a base for your character, you can still go ahead and retopologize'

[09:04] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'it. To get even better results, what we can do basically back in ComfyUI is that we\'re choosing here our resolution. So, we can for example increase our'

[09:17] [scene:talk]
