VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'lot of holes in your mesh, you can change here the level to something lower, so something like 0.4 for example. One more thing I\'m always checking is that you have here the number of Gaussian set to the max number that we have over here. Quickly also put'

[09:43] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
