[09:56] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'range. We have a 65K range for medium, and for high quality, 130K. This is already the maximum we have by default. What is basically shown here, which is this a number over here. You can, of'

[10:09] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'course, also play around with the seed to get different results. And you could even, you know, for the 3D file size. So, in case you would like to change it, you can change here the format, for example, also to ply, which is then basically a different format for you in'

[10:22] [scene:talk]
